dct_description_sm: Published at Washington D.C. December 1902 ; O.H. Tittmann, Superintendent.
Depths shown by soundings and spot shading, dotted lines.
Lights table, signs and abbreviations, tides table, storm warning displays.
Shows low water areas, coasts, waterways, vegetation, rocks, wrecks, buoys, city plan, railroads, buildings.
